*** MemoServ Help - Command: FORWARD ***
Forwards all memos comming to your current nick
to the one you have specified. The specified nick
to have memos being forwarded to must be registered
with NickServ and you must be identified to it.
Channel memo's will automatically be forwarded as well.
When NONE is given as nick, this option will be disabled.
 
Syntax:
/ms FORWARD nick
 
Examples:
/ms FORWARD Miki
/ms FORWARD NONE
 
Type /join #IRCHelp for more information.
*** End of Help ***